Package: biblioview
Title: A Shiny Web Portal and Abstract Enricher for Zotero Libraries
Version: 0.3.6
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Petzoldt", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "thomas.petzoldt@tu-dresden.de",
                     comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4951-6468"))         
Description: Provides automated pipelines to fetch Zotero group libraries, 
    generate APA citations, and harvest citation counts and missing abstracts
    from external metadata APIs (Crossref, OpenAlex, and Europe PMC).
License: GPL >= 2
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    purrr
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
URL: https://tpetzoldt.github.io/biblioview/
